name: 3BuBu
description: 3BuBu is a Matrix-Driven Web3 Loop fusing powerful DeFi mechanics, vibrant Meme culture, and emotional storytelling into a decentralized, community-centric financial universe. Taking inspiration from the iconic toy Labubu, 3BuBu infuses its rebellious spirit into a dynamic, decentralized Metaverse driven by emotion. Within this universe, three distinct emotional characters come to life: Boombu – Bold and Energetic Crybu – Reflective and Empathetic Deadbu – Rational and Pragmatic These characters embody emotional identities, unlock economic opportunities, and inspire collaborative IP creation within our unique ecosystem.
